<span id="freeTextContainer2124896807050396958">Ok, after a good night sleep, I can tell how I feel about this book. <br/>I don&apos;t think I&apos;ve ever read a book that had me feeling so many emotions AT ONE TIME. <br/>There were times I was LMAO with tears rolling down my face. Once, towards the end, I was sobbing so hard, I was afraid my husband would hear me in the next room. <br/>AWESOME AWESOME AWESOME book!!!!</span>
  <span id="freeText2124896807050396958" style="display:none">Ok, after a good night sleep, I can tell how I feel about this book. <br />I don't think I've ever read a book that had me feeling so many emotions AT ONE TIME. <br />There were times I was LMAO with tears rolling down my face. Once, towards the end, I was sobbing so hard, I was afraid my husband would hear me in the next room. <br />AWESOME AWESOME AWESOME book!!!!</span>
